comments: Anthony (POR) makes marginal contact with Finney-Smith's (DAL) while setting the pick.
Porzingis (DAL) is already in Trent Jr.'s (POR) path and he rolls to the rim after the defenders have switched.

Replay review of the foul called on Porzingis (DAL) pursuant to a coach's challenge was unsuccessful. The offensive foul stands on Porzingis because he grabs Trent's (POR) jersey and dislodges him in the post.
Trent Jr. (POR) is already in Finney-Smith's (DAL) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Doncic (DAL) is moving alongside Lillard's (POR) path and maintains a legal guarding position as he defends the drive.
Kleber (DAL) does not make contact to Whiteside's (POR) arm as he defends the shot near the rim.
The reaction from Trent Jr. (POR) is not consistent with the contact from Doncic (DAL).
Whiteside (POR) is moving alongside Doncic's (DAL) path and maintains a legal guarding position as he defends the drive.
Whiteside (POR) does not maintain legal guarding position and makes contact to Doncic's (DAL) head as he defends the shot attempt.
Lillard (POR) and Kleber (DAL) briefly engage and disengage during the inbound.
FInney-Smith (DAL) makes slight contact to Lillard's (POR) side as he defends the drive and the contact is marginal.
Kleber (DAL) cleanly deflects the ball away from Whiteside (POR) during rebounding.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) is already in Trent Jr.'s (POR) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) and McCollum (POR) briefly engage and disengage during the inbound.
Burke (DAL) veers into Lillard's (POR) path and delivers contact that affects Lillard's ability to defend the shot.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) commits a take foul on McCollum (POR).
McCollum (POR) legally contests Hardaway Jr.'s (DAL) jump shot attempt.
